# Documentation Governance

- `docs/` is canonical. `.cursor/plans/` is temporary.
- Update docs when architecture, invariants, or contracts change.
- Add or revise ADRs for major decisions about storage, orchestration, cutover, or ingestion path.
- Prefer concise, durable docs over scratch-note prose.
- Keep documentation aligned with the “maximum results and performance” philosophy.
